{
  "texts": [
    "Category Encoder.",
    "Many news platforms tag articles with hierarchical topic labels (e.g., categories and subcategories), which provide high-level semantic cues about the content.",
    "To incorporate this metadata, we encode both category ID v c and subcategory ID v sc via dense embeddings, initialized using DistilBERT and nonlinear projections: View-level Attention.",
    "Different views (e.g., title vs. abstract) may carry varying levels of informativeness depending on the news content.",
    "To adaptively integrate them, we use a view-level attention mechanism that assigns a relevance weight to each view."
  ]
}